        public boolean searchForRelease(java.lang.String artist,
                                java.lang.String website,
                                javafx.stage.Stage primaryStage)
        Searches a website using an artist's name and current date as parameters to find new music released by the artist for that day
        Parameters:
        artist - the artist's name
        website - the website url
        primaryStage - the main program window. Needed to create the invalid artist popup
        Returns:
        true if the artist has released music. False if an invalid artist is specified or an error loading the website occurs
